queries.sql: SELECT ROW_NUMBER() OVER() AS no, `tbl_riwayat_pengembalian`.`id` as `riwayat_id`, `tbl_peminjaman`.`id` as `peminjaman_id`, `tbl_peminjaman`.`kode_pinjam`, `tbl_peminjaman`.`user_id`, `tbl_peminjaman`.`nama_peminjam`, `tbl_peminjaman`.`tanggal_pinjam`, `tbl_peminjaman`.`keperluan`, `kode_kembali`, `tanggal_kembali`, `keterangan`, `tbl_barang`.`nama_barang`, `tbl_barang`.`kode_barang`, `tbl_riwayat_pengembalian`.`peminjaman_id`, `tbl_riwayat_pengembalian`.`barang_id` FROM `tbl_riwayat_pengembalian` JOIN `tbl_peminjaman` ON `tbl_peminjaman`.`id` = `tbl_riwayat_pengembalian`.`peminjaman_id` JOIN `tbl_barang` ON `tbl_barang`.`id` = `tbl_riwayat_pengembalian`.`barang_id` WHERE `tanggal_kembali` LIKE '2024%' ESCAPE '!' ORDER BY `tanggal_kembali` DESC
